@startuml state-event-flow

skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false

title Event Lifecycle - State Machine

[*] --> EventCreated : AggregateRoot.Apply()

EventCreated : Event serialized to JSON
EventCreated : StoredEvent record created
EventCreated : Added to _storedEvents list

EventCreated --> EventStored : CoopDbContext.SavingChanges

EventStored : StoredEvent added to DbSet
EventStored : Persisted in same transaction
EventStored : Committed to StoredEvents table

EventStored --> EventPublished : CoopDbContext.SavedChanges

EventPublished : Deserialized back to domain type
EventPublished : Pushed via INotificationService.OnNext
EventPublished : Streamed to SSE clients
EventPublished : Aggregate._storedEvents cleared

EventPublished --> [*]

@enduml
